divs: Sighting DetailsI was pulling into my driveway from church and shopping.I observed a large black domed disk hovering over my neighbors house. It was thirty to fifty feet in diameter,dull black and moved slowly eastward.I observed it for 2-3 seconds before it "cloaked" or disappeared.
Summary: Disk sighted hovering over neighbors house. approx -30-50 feet in diameter.
